Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:54.39,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(460,488)}美瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:54.93,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了点料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.01,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了点料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:55.93,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了点料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.01,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了点料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.10,Kaguya_hm_FOT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\pos(1806,476)}稍微加了点料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,听说您是来探望辉夜大小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:05.36,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs80\b1\pos(378,926)}关于四宫辉夜①
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我带您去辉夜大小姐的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:14.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我就只是来给四宫送文件的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂小姐帮我送过去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了这了还害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不了不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:29.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是亲手交给辉夜大小姐比较妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐 有客人来看您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您在找什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂也想一起放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,着急的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但要先治好感冒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 有客人来看您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会长会在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 今天开始住我们家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不会住 不会住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂小姐这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,西格蒙德·弗洛伊德说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:37.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的行动是根据欲望和理性决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.24,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的本能会生出很多欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.87,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:45.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,理性是抑制欲望的刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.08,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.25,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H202228&\3c&HEDF6FD&}想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:52.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果因为某些原因失去作为理性源头的思考能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人就会变成欲望驱使的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是变成白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:17:59.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,越是平时用脑多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候反应越强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然看起来是醒着的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还像是在梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,生病时的事情全部都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和喝醉了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又是奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:26.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我差不多要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您照顾辉夜大小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:31.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点请您注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:36.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这个房间差不多3个小时都绝对不会有人来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:39.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:45.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这个房间隔音效果完美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:47.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐也不会记得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你做什么都不会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:56.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以绝对绝对不要做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带了一些喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:13.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:20.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 现在的四宫说话没有逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话我有点邪念期待她让我喂她之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她真的很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能能听到四宫真正的想法或者弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫 你是不是因为我才感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:41.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天你是想要送我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才在校门口等着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是又好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你生气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是生气啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:11.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是让会长为难
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:17.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我呀 一直都…不知道该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很多事都是第一次做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:27.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我只能用我会的方法
