Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.96,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad10\c&H7E1672&\fs180\4c&H1E1214&\pos(412.8,800)\c&H892876&\fad(400,0)}理\N性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在几点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉睡了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你为什么在我床上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来探病的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:51.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁会在床上探病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着别人睡觉 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人渣 滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶呀 果然变成这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:11.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 睡得真够死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我和会长到了哪一步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:17.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:21.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易 好不容易忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:23.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都这么努力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳不已的探病篇 完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:29.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嘛 应该是清白的吧…
